      "content": "i get that, but he's literally telling me he's fine. he's even drinking some water and saying he'll feel better in the morning if he just rests. honestly, he's always been a bit dramatic about stuff like this. if i just give him some aspirin or maybe a vitamin supplement to help with the fatigue, would that help fix whatever is going on? wouldn't it be better to just monitor him for a few hours first?",
